issue.title: TypeError: __init__() got an unexpected keyword argument 'population_size'
issue.body:
Got the following error while setting population_size argument in call to PySRRegressor(population_size=100), 

'TypeError: __init__() got an unexpected keyword argument 'population_size'

nodes.body: Bug is resolved in latest version of pysr. I upgraded to version 0.8.3 from 0.7.11.
